          This email may contain confidential information. If you are not the intended recipient(s) you are hereby notified that any dissemination, distribution or copying of this email message is strictly prohibited. If you have received this message in error, please immediately notify the sender and delete this email message from your computer. Information provided by Cohen Handler is never intended to be relied upon as specific investment advice and is not a substitute for such advice. The team at Cohen Handler are buyerâ€™s agents- not financial planners, investment advisers, accountants, or lawyers. Before taking any action or risking any money, you should always check with your own qualified professional advisers.
        </div>
      `;
    }

    // Update preview on input changes
    firstNameInput.addEventListener('input', updatePreview);
    lastNameInput.addEventListener('input', updatePreview);
    jobTitleInput.addEventListener('input', updatePreview);
    emailInput.addEventListener('input', updatePreview);
    phoneInput.addEventListener('input', updatePreview);

    // Initialize preview on page load
    updatePreview();
